1
00:00:25,130 --> 00:00:26,360
Archers, listen to my command.

2
00:00:26,360 --> 00:00:27,900
Aim at Ying Wujiu.

3
00:00:29,000 --> 00:00:30,130
Don't hurt the Lady,

4
00:00:30,130 --> 00:00:30,990
not even a hair.

5
00:00:31,260 --> 00:00:32,000
Shoot!

6
00:00:32,630 --> 00:00:34,030
Kill that eunuch!

7
00:00:35,200 --> 00:00:36,260
[Lanyue Pavilion]

8
00:00:47,700 --> 00:00:48,700
Jingzhi, don't be afraid.

9
00:00:48,700 --> 00:00:49,900
I'll take you out.

10
00:00:50,300 --> 00:00:51,400
They won't dare shoot you.

11
00:00:51,400 --> 00:00:52,660
Step on my shadow and go.

12
00:00:52,660 --> 00:00:53,960
Facing 3,000 imperial guards,

13
00:00:53,960 --> 00:00:55,200
I was reborn

14
00:00:55,300 --> 00:00:56,300
not to watch you

15
00:00:56,300 --> 00:00:57,400
die in front of me again.

16
00:00:57,400 --> 00:00:59,260
Ying Wujiu, you must stay alive to clear your name,

17
00:00:59,260 --> 00:01:00,660
and take back what is yours,

18
00:01:00,660 --> 00:01:01,900
instead of dying here.

19
00:01:01,900 --> 00:01:02,700
Leave it to me.

20
00:01:04,400 --> 00:01:06,400
Stop!

21
00:01:07,160 --> 00:01:08,860
All of you, stop!

22
00:01:16,430 --> 00:01:17,230
Your Majesty.

23
00:01:18,060 --> 00:01:21,160
Yu Henian has escaped from the capital through a secret passage.

24
00:01:21,160 --> 00:01:23,360
Once he returns to his private army camp,

25
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:25,200
100,000 private troops will rebel immediately.

26
00:01:25,200 --> 00:01:26,100
The letter in my hand

27
00:01:26,100 --> 00:01:27,400
is his only solid evidence.

28
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,600
Use this secret list

29
00:01:29,060 --> 00:01:31,360
in exchange for Ying Wujiu leading the troops.

30
00:01:31,360 --> 00:01:33,200
I will return to the palace with you

31
00:01:33,200 --> 00:01:34,259
to be your hostage.

32
00:01:35,430 --> 00:01:35,960
Jingzhi.

33
00:01:36,600 --> 00:01:38,330
I don't want you to trade your life for mine.

34
00:01:38,330 --> 00:01:40,460
Worst comes to worst, we die together.

35
00:01:40,630 --> 00:01:41,200
Jingzhi,

36
00:01:41,500 --> 00:01:42,630
put down the hairpin.

37
00:01:42,630 --> 00:01:43,630
I'll do as you say.

38
00:01:43,700 --> 00:01:45,160
I'll agree to whatever you want.

39
00:01:45,160 --> 00:01:46,000
Just for a

40
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,160
rootless eunuch,

41
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:48,660
would you throw your life away?

42
00:01:48,660 --> 00:01:49,460
Ying Wujiu,

43
00:01:49,759 --> 00:01:50,759
go to the border,

44
00:01:51,060 --> 00:01:52,160
and cut off the head

45
00:01:52,160 --> 00:01:54,000
of that old bastard Yu Henian.

46
00:01:54,000 --> 00:01:55,259
As for you,

47
00:01:56,100 --> 00:01:57,700
return to the palace with me.

48
00:01:58,360 --> 00:02:00,360
For every day he wins at the border,

49
00:02:00,360 --> 00:02:02,090
I will let you live another day.

50
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:03,890
If he dies in battle,

51
00:02:03,930 --> 00:02:05,800
I will have you buried with him.

52
00:02:07,030 --> 00:02:08,500
Go, Ying Wujiu.

53
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:11,020
Take control of your military power.

54
00:02:11,530 --> 00:02:12,860
Here in the deep palace,

55
00:02:13,330 --> 00:02:14,960
I will guard the rear for you.

56
00:02:29,329 --> 00:02:31,829
Go, Jingzhi.

57
00:02:31,829 --> 00:02:33,530
Go see off Dazheng's hero.

58
00:02:34,100 --> 00:02:35,829
Don't keep me waiting too long.

59
00:02:46,660 --> 00:02:49,130
I wish the Director a swift victory

60
00:02:49,460 --> 00:02:51,260
and a speedy triumphant return.

61
00:02:56,500 --> 00:02:58,560
Jingzhi, wait for me.

62
00:02:59,900 --> 00:03:01,300
When I return in triumph,

63
00:03:01,760 --> 00:03:03,290
I'll get you out of the cage.

64
00:03:11,060 --> 00:03:12,800
All troops, listen to my command.

65
00:03:12,800 --> 00:03:13,800
Break camp!

66
00:03:18,460 --> 00:03:20,300
Look, Jingzhi.

67
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:23,100
He's gone. From now on,

68
00:03:23,260 --> 00:03:25,930
there's only you and me in this deep palace.

69
00:03:26,300 --> 00:03:28,530
You'll be a good girl in my cage, right?

70
00:03:28,730 --> 00:03:30,730
Helan Ci, little do you know,

71
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,500
that what you brought back

72
00:03:31,500 --> 00:03:34,300
is a poisonous snake that can bite your throat off.

73
00:03:36,260 --> 00:03:38,060
My lady, it is time to rest.

74
00:03:38,460 --> 00:03:39,630
His Majesty ordered

75
00:03:39,829 --> 00:03:42,360
that I must watch you drink this calming soup.

76
00:03:49,560 --> 00:03:51,530
The Eastern Depot's Shadow Tianzi undercover agent,

77
00:03:51,530 --> 00:03:52,829
pays respects to the Master.

78
00:03:52,829 --> 00:03:54,260
Please give your orders.

79
00:03:54,460 --> 00:03:56,900
Helan Ci thinks that taking Ying Wujiu away

80
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:59,360
will make this capital his world.

81
00:03:59,930 --> 00:04:02,300
Aunt, check a list for me.

82
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:05,760
I will make the Yu family's civil officials in the capital

83
00:04:05,760 --> 00:04:07,260
have no peace

84
00:04:07,560 --> 00:04:09,060
within three days.

85
00:04:10,500 --> 00:04:11,230
Jingzhi.

86
00:04:11,860 --> 00:04:13,600
Ying Wujiu fell into

87
00:04:13,700 --> 00:04:15,230
Yu Henian's ambush at Luori Slope

88
00:04:15,230 --> 00:04:16,700
and suffered heavy casualties.

89
00:04:16,700 --> 00:04:18,000
Guess if his heart will be

90
00:04:18,000 --> 00:04:20,529
pierced by arrows tonight.

91
00:04:20,529 --> 00:04:21,660
Whether he dies or not,

92
00:04:21,660 --> 00:04:22,930
I don't care.

93
00:04:23,230 --> 00:04:25,760
I only beg Your Majesty to let him die a little later.

94
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:27,060
At least until he chops off the head

95
00:04:27,060 --> 00:04:29,860
of that old thief Yu Henian for me.

96
00:04:30,530 --> 00:04:32,659
Excellent.

97
00:04:32,760 --> 00:04:34,500
As long as he is not in your heart,

98
00:04:34,500 --> 00:04:37,030
I don't care how many pieces he is hacked into.

99
00:04:56,700 --> 00:05:00,700
Withholding military rations is cutting off his survival.

100
00:05:03,830 --> 00:05:07,360
Aunt, Liu Yong has a highly favored concubine

101
00:05:07,860 --> 00:05:10,260
who got pregnant three days ago, right?

102
00:05:10,860 --> 00:05:13,320
Mobilize our assassins outside the palace.

103
00:05:14,430 --> 00:05:16,330
Yes, I will do it right away.

104
00:05:16,330 --> 00:05:17,430
Tonight at midnight,

105
00:05:17,430 --> 00:05:19,860
I want to see Liu Yong's suicide note,

106
00:05:19,860 --> 00:05:21,060
along with solid evidence of him hoarding weapons

107
00:05:21,060 --> 00:05:23,200
to support Yu Henian's rebellion,

108
00:05:23,200 --> 00:05:25,330
neatly placed on the Emperor's desk.

109
00:05:25,330 --> 00:05:28,530
To protect the man risking his life at the border,

110
00:05:28,560 --> 00:05:30,300
I don't mind turning into

111
00:05:30,500 --> 00:05:32,460
the cruelest demon in this palace.
